	1] Extract the archive in a folder on the Gothmog computer
	
	2] Compile the files just by using the "make" command (while being in the same folder as before)
	
	3] Use the program by using the command "OMP_NUM_THREADS=X ./max_subarray Tests/test_input_Y.in"
	where X is the number of threads you want to use and Y the size of the square matrix you ish to 
	compute (remember to make sure the file exists before, or the program will abort)	
	
